text: Argodrepana auratifrons is a moth in the family Drepanidae. It was described by William Warren in 1922. It is found in New Guinea.The Hooktips (Drepanidae, Drepaninae) of Papua Indonesia ==References== Category:Moths described in 1922 Category:Drepaninae Category:Moths of New Guinea
title: Argodrepana auratifrons
